Package: PlacidoApp
Title: Shiny Application for Quality Control Calculations Based on Spanish
    Royal Decree 1801/2008
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David A.", "Leo", , "david.leoacedo@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: PlacidoApp is a package that provides a Shiny application for
    performing quality control calculations in accordance with Spanish
    Royal Decree 1801/2008, dated November 3rd. This regulation
    establishes rules pertaining to nominal quantities for prepackaged
    products and the control of their actual content in Spain. The
    application allows users to input prepackaged product data and
    determine compliance with the standards set forth in the Royal Decree.
    Additionally, the application provides visualizations and summaries to
    facilitate the interpretation of the results.
